WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 22=

01:41.180 --> 01:42.020
Mr. Zhou.

01:43.620 --> 01:44.490
How did you know...

02:07.410 --> 02:08.250
Mr. Zhou,

02:08.980 --> 02:09.820
please sit.

02:24.010 --> 02:24.850
Mr. Zhou,

02:25.130 --> 02:26.170
have some tea.

02:31.570 --> 02:32.610
May I ask

02:33.340 --> 02:35.260
what troubles you so deeply?

02:38.410 --> 02:39.610
I have a sworn sister.

02:40.660 --> 02:42.560
When she was little,
her family fell into ruin.

02:43.850 --> 02:45.340
Her father and brothers were foolish.

02:45.340 --> 02:46.820
Her stepmother was cruel.

02:46.820 --> 02:49.340
So, she sought refuge
in my home at a young age.

02:51.850 --> 02:54.100
We grew up eating and living together,

02:54.100 --> 02:55.290
playing and laughing.

02:56.290 --> 02:58.780
We had so much fun.

02:58.780 --> 03:00.820
I thought that when we grew up,
I'd marry her.

03:01.500 --> 03:03.130
But when I was 12,

03:04.850 --> 03:07.290
my father suddenly arranged
a marriage for me.

03:07.835 --> 03:09.295
Then my grandmother ordered my sister

03:09.306 --> 03:10.610
to move out of my courtyard.

03:10.610 --> 03:12.540
We were no longer allowed to be close.

03:13.820 --> 03:14.730
Are you dissatisfied

03:15.780 --> 03:17.220
with this betrothal?

03:17.220 --> 03:18.060
I don't know.

03:18.730 --> 03:20.260
The family I'm betrothed to

03:20.260 --> 03:22.220
is a long-standing match for ours.

03:23.010 --> 03:24.423
My future father- and mother-in-law

03:24.434 --> 03:25.660
are kind and sensible people.

03:27.660 --> 03:29.260
The girl I'm engaged to

03:30.290 --> 03:31.260
is very good.

03:31.780 --> 03:32.660
Very good.

03:34.850 --> 03:35.730
My mother says

03:36.380 --> 03:37.940
that as long as I marry her,

03:39.100 --> 03:40.890
I can secure my future position.

03:43.780 --> 03:44.940
No one would dare object.

03:45.290 --> 03:46.570
So, Mr. Zhou,

03:47.380 --> 03:48.340
does the position matter

03:49.130 --> 03:49.970
to you?

03:50.170 --> 03:51.610
I don't care about that.

03:51.770 --> 03:53.060
I'd rather live freely,

03:53.080 --> 03:54.340
drifting across the rivers.

03:54.340 --> 03:55.690
So, to you,

03:55.690 --> 03:57.500
between your sister and your fiancée,

03:57.500 --> 03:59.170
who can't live without you?

04:02.170 --> 04:03.010
Yuqi,

04:03.230 --> 04:05.260
I'm not ready to marry yet.

04:05.260 --> 04:06.940
Do you wish to postpone it,

04:06.940 --> 04:08.570
or do you not wish to marry me at all?

04:08.570 --> 04:10.410
I don't wish

04:10.410 --> 04:11.610
to rush into marriage.

04:17.610 --> 04:18.610
Yuqi,

04:19.780 --> 04:20.620
I won't marry.

04:21.490 --> 04:22.503
If that day truly comes,

04:24.140 --> 04:25.220
I'll become a nun.

04:29.610 --> 04:31.050
The girl I'm engaged to

04:33.170 --> 04:34.140
is clever,

04:34.700 --> 04:35.580
beautiful,

04:36.340 --> 04:37.540
and capable.

04:39.540 --> 04:40.780
Even without me,

04:43.020 --> 04:45.540
she'll surely find a better match.

04:48.290 --> 04:49.980
But if my sister loses me,

04:51.370 --> 04:53.050
she'll have no way to survive.

04:53.900 --> 04:54.900
Isn't that the answer?

04:56.020 --> 04:57.850
The futures and happiness

04:58.410 --> 04:59.660
of the three people

05:00.540 --> 05:02.730
depend on your choice alone.

05:03.610 --> 05:05.140
You should decide soon.

05:11.410 --> 05:12.250
Here.

05:13.660 --> 05:14.900
The weather is dry.

05:15.780 --> 05:17.050
Your breath is unsteady.

05:17.980 --> 05:18.946
Have more tea.

05:20.850 --> 05:21.930
Thank you, sir.

05:41.340 --> 05:42.610
You are right.

05:42.610 --> 05:43.660
I should decide soon.

06:00.886 --> 06:01.986
What did you put in the tea?

06:03.050 --> 06:05.220
It's called the Coward's Courage.

06:05.220 --> 06:06.780
It makes one's blood surge,

06:06.780 --> 06:08.109
filling the heart with ambition,

06:08.120 --> 06:09.140
itching to fight at once.

06:09.930 --> 06:11.340
The Young Lord Zhou

06:11.340 --> 06:12.290
needs

06:12.290 --> 06:13.660
a little courage right now.

06:40.170 --> 06:41.010
Yours.

06:42.580 --> 06:43.890
- Yours.
- Thanks.

06:44.700 --> 06:45.540
Yours.

06:46.540 --> 06:48.410
And yours.

06:51.170 --> 06:52.170
Thank you, sir.

07:03.580 --> 07:04.850
You want to marry someone else?

07:05.980 --> 07:06.980
Over my dead body.

07:27.540 --> 07:28.660
Zhao,

07:30.980 --> 07:32.100
Zhuo and I

07:32.100 --> 07:33.850
did something big for you today.

07:34.177 --> 07:35.748
The mosquito balm samples has arrived.

07:35.759 --> 07:36.599
Over there.

07:37.410 --> 07:38.940
Really? I'll go take a look.

07:41.140 --> 07:41.980
Zhao.

07:42.370 --> 07:43.290
Yuqi.

07:46.140 --> 07:47.100
Yuqi,

07:48.290 --> 07:49.130
what are you doing?

07:52.020 --> 07:52.980
Zhao,

07:52.980 --> 07:53.850
we need to talk.

07:54.586 --> 07:55.805
I wish to cancel our betrothal.

07:55.930 --> 07:56.770
Cancel?

07:57.340 --> 07:58.180
Zhao,

07:58.370 --> 07:59.210
I'm sorry.

07:59.660 --> 08:01.780
This thought has been
in my heart for years.

08:01.780 --> 08:02.886
You are exceptional

08:02.897 --> 08:03.893
in talent and appearance.

08:04.730 --> 08:05.850
I'm mediocre.

08:06.850 --> 08:07.980
I truly don't deserve you.

08:08.410 --> 08:09.340
Why exactly?

08:10.050 --> 08:11.490
All these years in sparring,

08:11.490 --> 08:12.930
you knocked me down every time.

08:13.400 --> 08:14.900
My martial arts are inferior to yours.

08:14.900 --> 08:16.170
I'm not as decisive as you.

08:16.170 --> 08:17.580
You surpass me in every way.

08:17.580 --> 08:19.700
But I don't want a wife
who is stronger than I am.

08:19.700 --> 08:20.780
I hope my wife

08:22.250 --> 08:23.170
is understanding,

08:23.810 --> 08:24.900
gentle, and virtuous.

08:24.900 --> 08:26.700
Why not just say Min Xinrou's name?

08:26.700 --> 08:28.170
I do care for Xinrou.

08:32.340 --> 08:33.180
That's a rat.

08:34.180 --> 08:35.610
What is going on?

08:35.610 --> 08:36.940
I'm not holding a blade

08:36.940 --> 08:38.820
to your throat to force you to marry.

08:38.820 --> 08:40.180
Even if you held a blade to me,

08:40.482 --> 08:41.815
I'd still break off the betrothal.

08:41.980 --> 08:42.820
Zhou Yuqi,

08:43.980 --> 08:44.820
have you

08:45.530 --> 08:46.820
thought this through?

08:46.820 --> 08:47.700
I have.

08:50.420 --> 08:51.260
Zhao,

08:51.890 --> 08:53.420
I beg you to let me go.

09:02.820 --> 09:03.660
Very well.

09:04.820 --> 09:06.130
Since you have decided,

09:07.180 --> 09:08.340
the betrothal

09:09.850 --> 09:11.220
is hereby canceled.

09:17.530 --> 09:18.370
Please leave.

09:20.650 --> 09:22.130
Thanks for granting it, Zhao.

09:26.530 --> 09:28.900
I'll beat this heartless man to death.

09:28.910 --> 09:29.770
Xingjia.

09:29.770 --> 09:31.010
You...

09:31.010 --> 09:31.850
Calm down.

09:32.370 --> 09:34.370
This is intolerable.

09:39.250 --> 09:40.090
Young Master,

09:40.890 --> 09:42.730
I'll spread the news of Zhou Yuqi

09:42.730 --> 09:43.850
canceling the betrothal.

09:43.850 --> 09:45.370
I guarantee the entire town

09:45.890 --> 09:46.940
and the whole Jianghu

09:47.700 --> 09:48.820
will know.

09:52.060 --> 09:55.740
(Kind and Hospitable)

10:05.850 --> 10:07.340
Were we not returning to Qingque Sect?

10:07.820 --> 10:09.100
Why is everyone staring at me?

10:12.266 --> 10:13.459
The betrothal is truly broken?

10:16.770 --> 10:17.610
Zhuo,

10:18.010 --> 10:19.130
how did you know?

10:19.130 --> 10:20.580
The whole town knows.

10:21.420 --> 10:23.010
They say Young Lord Zhou knelt

10:23.010 --> 10:24.930
and begged you to spare him.

10:24.930 --> 10:25.770
He was always

10:25.770 --> 10:27.530
so attentive and considerate toward you.

10:27.530 --> 10:28.890
How could he suddenly break it off?

10:29.340 --> 10:30.770
Did you do something

10:30.770 --> 10:31.820
that frightened him?

10:31.820 --> 10:33.130
You are making things up.

10:33.130 --> 10:34.650
We parted on good terms.

10:34.650 --> 10:36.270
If you don't believe me, ask him.

10:36.340 --> 10:37.770
I went to find Zhou Yuqi.

10:37.770 --> 10:38.850
He is not in his room.

10:39.300 --> 10:40.140
Perhaps

10:40.700 --> 10:41.700
he went for a walk.

10:43.730 --> 10:45.370
Are you asking about Mr. Zhou?

10:46.370 --> 10:47.300
Early this morning,

10:47.300 --> 10:48.820
he boarded a carriage with a young lady

10:48.820 --> 10:49.660
and already left.

10:49.680 --> 10:51.250
He said he'd inform the elders.

10:53.100 --> 10:53.940
Men

10:56.850 --> 10:58.220
are indeed all worthless.

11:14.980 --> 11:15.820
You all eat first.

11:16.130 --> 11:17.340
I'll go for a walk.

11:18.700 --> 11:19.940
You are not eating at all?

11:27.940 --> 11:29.730
Xingjia truly has a big mouth.

11:33.890 --> 11:34.730
That is not right.

11:35.370 --> 11:37.060
He was with me the whole time.

11:49.490 --> 11:50.330
Zhao, you're here.

11:52.770 --> 11:53.770
Was it you who spread

11:53.770 --> 11:55.180
the news of my broken betrothal?

11:55.180 --> 11:57.010
I merely made a choice for you.

11:57.700 --> 11:58.730
You're so clever.

11:59.300 --> 12:00.530
You did not like Mr. Zhou

12:00.530 --> 12:01.580
and did not wish to marry.

12:02.010 --> 12:03.220
You hinted at me several times

12:03.580 --> 12:05.060
to push him a little.

12:05.770 --> 12:08.180
I only went along with the flow

12:08.180 --> 12:09.180
to fulfill your wish.

12:09.180 --> 12:10.370
It benefits all sides.

12:10.370 --> 12:11.370
Why not?

12:11.444 --> 12:12.948
How do you know that I don't like him

12:12.959 --> 12:14.049
and don't wish to marry him?

12:14.060 --> 12:15.039
Do you like the splendor

12:15.050 --> 12:17.130
and wealth of Peiqiong Manor

12:17.130 --> 12:19.420
or Mr. Zhou's thoughtfulness?

12:20.180 --> 12:21.020
If you ask me,

12:21.370 --> 12:22.843
you're not even as good as Zhou Yuqi.

12:23.530 --> 12:25.530
At least he truly wishes
to marry Min Xinrou.

12:26.340 --> 12:28.730
But you don't even know what you want.

12:28.730 --> 12:29.570
Shut up.

12:31.100 --> 12:33.100
There is no Zhou Yuqi in your heart.

12:33.730 --> 12:34.820
There is only me.

12:35.850 --> 12:37.490
You simply dare not admit it.

12:41.580 --> 12:43.300
Don't flatter yourself.

12:44.020 --> 12:44.890
You can like anyone

12:44.890 --> 12:46.100
as you please.

12:46.100 --> 12:47.610
We'll go our separate ways.

12:47.610 --> 12:48.980
May we never meet again.

12:49.940 --> 12:51.073
I heard Hexagonal Persimmons

12:51.084 --> 12:53.090
are mostly produced
in the southeast three states.

12:53.490 --> 12:56.220
I must find the Shi brothers.

12:56.220 --> 12:57.340
But how?

12:58.300 --> 13:00.530
I can only send out all my followers

13:00.890 --> 13:02.530
to make a grand search

13:02.530 --> 13:05.180
and turn the three states upside down.

13:05.820 --> 13:06.660
Besides,

13:07.490 --> 13:08.770
many people in Jianghu

13:09.300 --> 13:10.340
are eager

13:10.340 --> 13:11.940
to find the Shi brothers.

13:12.770 --> 13:14.580
If I spread the news...

13:14.580 --> 13:15.420
Don't you dare.

13:18.060 --> 13:19.530
So, you turned back after all.

13:21.980 --> 13:22.940
Zhao,

13:25.180 --> 13:27.220
Young Lord Zhou and Miss Min are back.

13:29.700 --> 13:30.540
Zhao?

13:45.730 --> 13:46.570
Yuzhi,

13:47.130 --> 13:47.886
I'm fine.

13:47.897 --> 13:49.060
I did not try to harm myself.

13:49.060 --> 13:50.340
I did not become a nun.

13:50.340 --> 13:51.730
I just went out to clear my head.

13:52.220 --> 13:53.650
Please don't worry.

13:54.490 --> 13:56.420
Zhou Yuqi and I decided
to cancel the betrothal.

13:57.100 --> 13:58.530
Don't give him a hard time.

13:59.300 --> 14:01.420
(From Cai Zhao)

14:05.620 --> 14:06.480
Everything

14:06.480 --> 14:07.850
is all my fault.

14:07.850 --> 14:08.980
Don't hurt Yuqi.

14:09.530 --> 14:11.420
We've wronged Zhao,

14:11.420 --> 14:13.010
so we came back

14:13.010 --> 14:14.313
to apologize to her.

14:14.324 --> 14:15.982
What's the use of that?
He deserves this.

14:15.993 --> 14:17.180
What are you doing?

14:17.180 --> 14:18.370
We should cherish beauty.

14:19.180 --> 14:20.700
Talk it out properly.

14:23.650 --> 14:24.490
Yuqi,

14:24.820 --> 14:25.660
are you alright?

14:28.650 --> 14:29.530
Lingbo,

14:30.530 --> 14:31.370
I'm fine.

14:31.730 --> 14:32.820
That is good.

14:37.650 --> 14:38.490
Yuqi!

14:38.700 --> 14:40.340
Zhao suffered so much grievance.

14:40.340 --> 14:41.580
A single apology is enough?

14:46.610 --> 14:47.850
I alone bear the consequences.

14:48.370 --> 14:49.220
All faults

14:49.220 --> 14:50.100
are mine.

14:50.370 --> 14:51.340
Beat me to death.

14:51.850 --> 14:52.700
I won't regret it.

15:00.060 --> 15:01.980
Don't hit my Yuqi.

15:01.980 --> 15:03.850
Don't ruin his peerless face.

15:05.039 --> 15:06.279
You came to beat me too, right?

15:11.540 --> 15:12.540
(From Cai Zhao)

15:14.250 --> 15:16.850
Zhao only said
she went out to clear her head.

15:16.850 --> 15:19.180
It does not mean she left with Mr. Mu.

15:19.180 --> 15:21.010
The innkeeper told me

15:21.010 --> 15:22.420
that Master You came earlier

15:22.420 --> 15:24.700
and packed up everything
from Zhao's room.

15:25.770 --> 15:26.610
He said

15:27.180 --> 15:28.420
she might need them.

15:28.730 --> 15:30.370
I knew you were hiding something.

15:30.820 --> 15:32.700
Did Cai Zhao elope with Mu Qingyan?

15:32.700 --> 15:34.130
What eloping?

15:34.130 --> 15:35.370
Don't talk nonsense.

15:35.370 --> 15:37.242
Zhao was only upset

15:37.253 --> 15:38.580
and went out to clear her head.

15:38.580 --> 15:39.580
Xingjia,

15:39.580 --> 15:41.530
I've been watching the demonic sect.

15:41.530 --> 15:43.420
This morning,

15:43.420 --> 15:45.250
they suddenly withdrew from the town.

15:45.250 --> 15:46.980
Zhao happened to go out
at the same time.

15:47.770 --> 15:48.650
Could it be

15:49.370 --> 15:51.130
just a coincidence?

15:51.130 --> 15:51.970
Yes.

15:52.120 --> 15:53.446
That's too much of a coincidence.

15:53.820 --> 15:55.340
Though Zhou Yuqi is no good,

15:56.180 --> 15:57.580
if Cai Zhao therefore

15:57.580 --> 15:59.300
colludes with the demonic sect,

15:59.300 --> 16:00.940
the crime would be even worse.

16:02.580 --> 16:03.420
Remember:

16:03.980 --> 16:05.890
Zhao only went out to clear her head.

16:05.890 --> 16:07.650
She has nothing to do
with the demonic sect.

16:07.650 --> 16:09.340
Song Yuzhi, what's wrong with you?

16:09.340 --> 16:11.340
First,, you cooperated with Mu Qingyan.

16:11.340 --> 16:12.920
Now, you openly shield Cai Zhao.

16:12.931 --> 16:14.705
Have you lost your sense
of right and wrong?

16:14.716 --> 16:15.953
Master will arrive in two days.

16:16.340 --> 16:17.220
No matter what,

16:17.220 --> 16:18.890
we'll meet him first.

16:19.980 --> 16:21.890
Besides, Nie Zhe may be nearby.

16:22.220 --> 16:23.060
Danger is everywhere.

16:24.580 --> 16:25.460
The priority

16:25.460 --> 16:26.850
is to find Zhao first,

16:26.850 --> 16:27.890
in case something happens.

16:30.100 --> 16:32.340
Elder Hu has been locked
in Bliss Palace,

16:32.340 --> 16:33.770
guarded by Shangguan Haonan.

16:34.370 --> 16:35.233
What about Mu Qingyan?

16:35.244 --> 16:36.506
He hasn't returned to the sect.

16:36.517 --> 16:38.490
I heard he left with Cai Zhao.

16:39.140 --> 16:40.010
You may go.

16:40.010 --> 16:40.850
Yes.

16:43.580 --> 16:46.130
Mu Qingyan indeed has some ability.

16:46.130 --> 16:48.060
He even colluded with the Six Sects.

16:48.650 --> 16:49.490
Cai Zhao

16:50.650 --> 16:51.610
can't be left alive.

16:52.060 --> 16:53.010
Rest assured, Chief.

16:54.940 --> 16:56.370
I'll send someone at once.

17:00.250 --> 17:01.850
Sending Hu Fengge

17:01.850 --> 17:03.850
was not enough for Mu Qingyan?

17:03.850 --> 17:05.380
You want to send more?

17:09.180 --> 17:10.940
This time, you need not act.

17:12.180 --> 17:13.660
Just wait to collect

17:14.180 --> 17:15.090
Mu Qingyan's corpse.

17:15.420 --> 17:16.260
Yes.

17:22.989 --> 17:24.876
This is the map
of the southeast three states.

17:25.530 --> 17:26.530
We start here

17:27.010 --> 17:28.940
and follow this road all the way.

17:29.530 --> 17:30.960
Places that produce persimmons

17:30.971 --> 17:32.420
must have fertile land and people.

17:32.420 --> 17:33.860
The villages and towns along the way

17:33.860 --> 17:35.570
should all be searched.

17:35.570 --> 17:36.730
Zhao, do you know

17:36.730 --> 17:37.940
how vast

17:38.260 --> 17:39.480
the southeast three states are?

17:43.980 --> 17:44.940
It seems

17:45.940 --> 17:46.780
quite large.

17:47.090 --> 17:48.290
Within those states,

17:48.730 --> 17:50.860
how many villages and towns are there?

17:59.420 --> 18:00.660
Only a few hundred.

18:04.620 --> 18:05.490
Right now, we have

18:05.490 --> 18:07.083
only the Hexagonal Persimmons as a clue.

18:07.330 --> 18:08.330
What else can we do?

18:08.810 --> 18:10.700
Do you have a better idea?

18:10.980 --> 18:11.820
No.

18:14.660 --> 18:15.730
I'll follow you.

18:31.380 --> 18:32.220
Let's go.

18:33.090 --> 18:34.140
My legs are numb.

19:29.290 --> 19:30.490
After crossing that mountain,

19:30.490 --> 19:32.180
we should reach the next village.

19:32.180 --> 19:33.020
If we had just

19:33.770 --> 19:35.050
crossed the river earlier,

19:35.846 --> 19:37.046
would it not have been faster?

19:40.090 --> 19:41.270
Didn't you hear the villagers?

19:41.980 --> 19:43.220
The heavy rain these days

19:43.220 --> 19:44.180
washed away the bridge.

19:45.180 --> 19:46.693
Climbing the mountain is the shortcut.

20:45.050 --> 20:46.620
Cooperating with Mu Qingyan

20:46.940 --> 20:48.330
was solely my decision.

20:48.770 --> 20:50.220
I'm willing to accept punishment.

20:50.220 --> 20:51.220
- You...
- Master.

20:58.090 --> 20:58.930
Forget it.

20:59.180 --> 21:00.050
I'm also at fault.

21:01.900 --> 21:04.530
I've been so protective of you

21:05.090 --> 21:07.250
that you don't know
how dangerous Jianghu is.

21:08.290 --> 21:09.130
Yuzhi,

21:09.660 --> 21:10.570
answer me.

21:10.940 --> 21:12.940
Do you truly think Mu Qingyan

21:13.330 --> 21:14.250
is a good person?

21:16.420 --> 21:17.260
He...

21:18.420 --> 21:19.420
He's never done evil.

21:19.420 --> 21:20.700
That is in public.

21:20.700 --> 21:21.660
What about in private?

21:22.093 --> 21:23.349
The identity of the man in black

21:23.360 --> 21:24.380
is still a mystery.

21:25.010 --> 21:26.180
You believe

21:26.180 --> 21:27.980
he is the one who massacred
the Chang clan.

21:28.380 --> 21:30.770
But that's only Mu Qingyan's story.

21:30.770 --> 21:32.220
You've been to the fort.

21:32.220 --> 21:33.940
You should know its mechanisms

21:33.940 --> 21:35.290
are unparalleled in the world.

21:35.290 --> 21:37.730
To break them, there is only one way:

21:37.730 --> 21:40.050
working from someone inside.

21:40.730 --> 21:41.860
Are you saying...?

21:42.180 --> 21:43.530
Chang was honest and kind.

21:44.290 --> 21:46.010
He likely let a wolf into the house.

21:46.530 --> 21:47.370
Master, you're right.

21:47.810 --> 21:48.856
People of the demonic sect

21:48.900 --> 21:49.740
can never be trusted.

21:50.620 --> 21:52.290
Mu Qingyan disguised himself
as Chang Ning

21:52.290 --> 21:53.420
and infiltrated Qingque Sect.

21:53.787 --> 21:55.933
His ambition is vicious
and not to be underestimated.

21:57.940 --> 21:58.780
Master,

21:59.620 --> 22:00.660
could Zhao

22:01.620 --> 22:03.620
have been taken by Mu Qingyan?

22:03.620 --> 22:04.530
Even if she was taken,

22:04.980 --> 22:06.953
she only has herself to blame
for misjudging him.

22:07.810 --> 22:09.010
This matter is serious.

22:09.810 --> 22:10.900
Don't spread it publicly.

22:11.380 --> 22:13.420
Just say she went wandering

22:13.420 --> 22:14.770
to clear her mind.

22:15.490 --> 22:17.730
You will investigate in secret.

22:17.730 --> 22:18.770
If you find

22:18.770 --> 22:20.940
any demonic villains harassing her,

22:20.940 --> 22:22.290
kill them without mercy.

22:22.290 --> 22:23.130
Yes.

22:34.050 --> 22:34.890
Hungry?

22:37.140 --> 22:38.530
Out traveling,

22:39.010 --> 22:40.220
and still so particular.

23:00.330 --> 23:01.700
It'll rain soon.

23:03.490 --> 23:05.250
Let's find a place
to take shelter later.

23:07.770 --> 23:08.610
Alright.

23:53.700 --> 23:55.490
When can I tell you how much I miss you

23:56.290 --> 23:57.980
during the rain?

23:58.380 --> 23:59.700
In the past, I did not like rain.

24:00.660 --> 24:01.810
It felt damp and unpleasant.

24:03.330 --> 24:04.170
But today,

24:04.730 --> 24:05.770
I find it

24:07.330 --> 24:08.170
quite nice.

24:11.026 --> 24:12.679
The road will be slippery
after the rain.

24:13.140 --> 24:14.220
It seems we must

24:14.220 --> 24:15.490
stay here one more day.

24:16.770 --> 24:17.610
Where are you going?

24:18.700 --> 24:20.180
Since we're staying another day,

24:20.180 --> 24:21.810
I'll gather more firewood.

24:26.420 --> 24:27.460
(What's wrong with him?)

24:27.810 --> 24:29.220
(More calm than I am.)

25:14.330 --> 25:15.900
There may be wild beasts at night.

25:16.530 --> 25:18.090
I'll keep watch tonight.

26:33.810 --> 26:34.660
If

26:36.220 --> 26:37.980
we could always stay like this,

26:38.860 --> 26:39.810
roaming Jianghu,

26:41.010 --> 26:41.860
seeing the world,

26:44.860 --> 26:46.570
would that not be a beautiful thing?

26:53.620 --> 26:54.620
It would.

27:35.140 --> 27:35.980
Zhao,

27:36.420 --> 27:37.620
are you sure the Shi brothers

27:38.330 --> 27:39.250
are nearby?

27:39.900 --> 27:41.380
When I was little,

27:41.380 --> 27:42.833
I ate this kind of persimmon cake.

27:43.490 --> 27:44.860
They've secluded themselves

27:44.860 --> 27:46.420
in a very distant place.

27:47.290 --> 27:48.620
But the water we drink

27:49.860 --> 27:51.180
comes from the same river.

27:53.090 --> 27:54.063
Within the three states,

27:54.380 --> 27:55.700
only this Su River

27:55.700 --> 27:57.700
connects to Qingluo River
of Luoying Valley.

27:58.250 --> 27:59.090
However,

27:59.420 --> 28:01.730
there are dozens of towns
along this river.

28:01.730 --> 28:02.980
If we search one by one...

28:02.980 --> 28:03.820
No need.

28:04.140 --> 28:05.120
We only need to buy

28:05.131 --> 28:06.557
the persimmon cakes from each place.

28:07.900 --> 28:09.290
Once we find the same taste,

28:09.980 --> 28:11.090
we'll know

28:11.090 --> 28:12.940
where Uncle Shi is living in seclusion.

28:43.220 --> 28:44.060
The taste is close.

28:44.330 --> 28:45.243
They should be nearby.

28:45.520 --> 28:46.380
Buy more.

28:46.380 --> 28:47.460
I can eat ten more.

28:47.660 --> 28:48.500
Zhao,

28:49.220 --> 28:51.010
why not try again tomorrow?

28:51.920 --> 28:52.770
No.

28:52.770 --> 28:53.620
We must hurry.

29:03.490 --> 29:04.330
Don't move.

29:04.799 --> 29:06.032
Persimmons are cold in nature.

29:06.420 --> 29:07.480
They've hurt your stomach.

29:07.940 --> 29:10.090
I just used my inner power
to clear your meridians.

29:10.490 --> 29:11.810
Your inner power is unstable.

29:12.530 --> 29:13.530
If you keep eating,

29:13.810 --> 29:15.530
you may have diarrhea tonight.

29:15.530 --> 29:16.370
Diarrhea?

29:19.700 --> 29:21.330
You know quite a bit about medicine.

29:22.090 --> 29:23.090
Father read widely.

29:24.330 --> 29:25.660
I read many of his books.

29:28.420 --> 29:30.620
He only wished to leave
the Hanhai Mountains

29:31.700 --> 29:32.813
and stay away from Jianghu,

29:33.900 --> 29:35.700
so he learned many ways
to make a living.

29:37.180 --> 29:38.660
He once wanted to be a physician,

29:39.090 --> 29:40.180
journeying across the world,

29:41.330 --> 29:42.170
healing the sick.

29:42.420 --> 29:44.700
So, we had many medical books.

29:54.050 --> 29:56.070
Small trinkets!

29:56.530 --> 29:57.420
I've inquired already.

29:57.420 --> 29:58.270
Take a look.

29:58.280 --> 29:59.330
People in the neighborhood

29:59.940 --> 30:01.330
come here for the market.

30:01.330 --> 30:02.810
Come and see, everyone.

30:03.290 --> 30:06.180
These are weapons
passed down for generations.

30:06.180 --> 30:07.860
Today, I sell them at a low price.

30:07.860 --> 30:08.980
Don't miss this chance.

30:08.980 --> 30:09.900
Make way.

30:09.900 --> 30:10.653
Passers-by,

30:10.664 --> 30:11.610
don't miss this chance.

30:11.620 --> 30:12.700
Sir,

30:12.700 --> 30:14.730
lend me your stall for a day.

30:14.730 --> 30:15.570
How do I lend it?

30:15.570 --> 30:17.000
Fortune telling!

30:17.000 --> 30:18.440
Always accurate!

30:20.530 --> 30:22.010
Then I'll throw in another day.

30:22.010 --> 30:22.900
Small trinkets!

30:22.900 --> 30:24.220
Goodbye.

30:25.203 --> 30:26.896
This is not a place
that sells persimmons.

30:27.530 --> 30:28.570
Why rent it?

30:28.700 --> 30:30.006
You want to eat more persimmons?

30:30.700 --> 30:32.420
You are about to become one yourself.

30:34.660 --> 30:35.500
This time,

30:36.900 --> 30:38.140
we try another way.

30:40.420 --> 30:42.250
(Sunshine Blade)
Everyone, come and see.

30:42.730 --> 30:45.090
This Sunshine Blade
was left by an elder.

30:45.090 --> 30:46.730
If not for lacking travel funds,

30:46.730 --> 30:48.530
I'd never sell it cheap.

30:48.940 --> 30:50.490
Don't miss this chance.

30:50.940 --> 30:52.090
Passers-by,

30:52.090 --> 30:53.380
don't miss this chance.

30:57.380 --> 30:58.770
Why is no one interested?

31:02.660 --> 31:03.500
Zhao,

31:03.700 --> 31:05.133
if your aunt knew

31:05.144 --> 31:06.597
you were selling her blade like this,

31:06.940 --> 31:08.380
would she burst from her coffin?

31:11.420 --> 31:12.900
Was it not your bad idea?

31:14.730 --> 31:15.810
Tell me.

31:15.810 --> 31:16.980
Can this really lure

31:16.980 --> 31:18.700
Uncle Shi out?

31:18.700 --> 31:19.700
Even in seclusion,

31:20.770 --> 31:22.490
they still need daily supplies.

31:22.770 --> 31:23.900
And I have asked around.

31:23.900 --> 31:24.880
The Shi family is large.

31:25.660 --> 31:27.050
They must buy many things.

31:28.220 --> 31:29.570
By reason,

31:29.570 --> 31:30.900
they should come out

31:30.900 --> 31:32.380
to restock every month.

31:36.570 --> 31:37.700
Let me have a look.

31:41.380 --> 31:42.220
Here.

31:48.570 --> 31:50.330
The blade looks sharp.

31:50.620 --> 31:51.460
I'll test it.

31:53.860 --> 31:54.980
Sir, to be honest,

31:55.330 --> 31:57.090
this blade is best for cutting pork.

31:57.090 --> 31:58.290
It has slaughtered

31:58.290 --> 32:00.530
many animals.

32:03.810 --> 32:05.090
It may be ugly,

32:05.980 --> 32:06.820
but

32:07.290 --> 32:08.810
it cuts meat well enough.

32:08.810 --> 32:09.900
How is my blade ugly?

32:11.290 --> 32:12.420
You have good eyes, sir.

32:12.860 --> 32:14.730
Though this is a precious blade,

32:14.730 --> 32:15.810
the price is not high.

32:16.380 --> 32:17.220
How much?

32:17.900 --> 32:18.740
100,000 taels.

32:19.630 --> 32:20.490
How much?

32:20.490 --> 32:21.330
100,000 taels.

32:23.140 --> 32:24.570
Have you two gone mad for money?

32:25.050 --> 32:26.220
Swindlers.

32:27.290 --> 32:28.420
You wasted my time.

33:10.700 --> 33:11.540
Strange.

33:12.330 --> 33:13.530
Where did he go?

33:24.420 --> 33:25.330
So high.

33:49.730 --> 33:50.700
Nie Zhe is more impatient

33:50.700 --> 33:51.940
than I thought.

33:52.220 --> 33:53.330
Their positions are unusual.

33:54.180 --> 33:55.173
Be careful of formations.

34:44.860 --> 34:45.980
They are here for me.

34:46.300 --> 34:47.140
I'll hold them off.

34:47.380 --> 34:48.220
You go.

34:49.879 --> 34:51.079
(Qian position, Kun position.)

34:51.420 --> 34:53.340
(Why does it resemble
the Big Dipper Formation?)

35:02.340 --> 35:03.180
Go.

35:19.920 --> 35:30.580
=Generation to Generation=

35:49.340 --> 35:53.750
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

35:54.315 --> 35:58.930
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

35:59.270 --> 36:03.835
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

36:04.360 --> 36:08.660
♪Free to wander in the world♪

36:11.605 --> 36:16.305
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:16.830 --> 36:21.120
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

36:21.780 --> 36:25.810
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

36:26.125 --> 36:31.250
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

36:31.825 --> 36:36.635
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:36.850 --> 36:41.020
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:41.745 --> 36:45.680
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:46.180 --> 36:51.455
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

37:14.185 --> 37:19.315
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:19.680 --> 37:24.050
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

37:24.315 --> 37:28.445
♪I freely roam in the world♪

37:28.630 --> 37:34.205
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
